    "Nevertheless, these adjustments reflect our dedication to conducting a comprehensive and inclusive trial, ultimately contributing to a more nuanced understanding of chronic pain management.",
    "This may lead us to unforeseen modifications in our program.Despite widespread internet access in Canada, disparities in internet speed, affordability, and digital literacy persist.",
    "APM, being exclusively web-based, poses a limitation in reaching individuals from remote regions and Indigenous communities as well as those in low-income households, older adults, and individuals with disabilities.",
